body: it seems that the **Run OpenSudio** component can get the correct output variables for the same model: [](http://api.ning.com:80/files/e07SsrLQeQOZvSVk-zsX9UdRCNf-fK9H*p9U6YCxwLDN124Kb2ohvKU7s*zbi3RK1-rHm*4izpqjuuvzZhzZ4jPDxujXiNjZ/Image3.png) But the **top three output variables** and **mechanicalVentilationEnergy** variable are missing from the result file produced by the **Run EP simulation** component: [](http://api.ning.com:80/files/e07SsrLQeQPYdlqZJmsU82DXsjX71299iBrg65kPZ2xHBndBQP*sgE7UtT*hjZWQEaaXoNmqWLIelVXoSL-EPcWmwNQT8YjO/Image4.png) Appreciate if you can kindly advise the source of this issue, because we need to use the **Run EP Simulation** component to get the output related to PV generator, kind of urgently.... Thanks.
